						<summary>

						<p>Records the grant of land, by <hi rend="bold">Chandrāditya</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Chōḍa-vaṁśa,</hi> whose capital was <hi rend="bold">Bārasūra,</hi> to the temple of Chandrādityēśvara established by him on the bund of the tank Chandrāditya-Samudra, also constructed by him during the reign of the <hi rend="bold">Chinda</hi> king <hi rend="bold">Jagadēkabhūshaṇa.</hi></p>						

						<p>First Side.</p>						

						</summary>
